<p>
Breaking transactions down by type, the XRPL processed <b>68,216,082</b> total payments last year, with an average of <b>5,684,673.5</b> per month. The number of payments in November (<b>34,103,937</b>) dwarfed of the previous months combined (<b>17,023,428</b>) by a factor of 100%. There was less variance in the number of offers created by month (total: <b>209,979,957</b>), the standard deviation being: <b>7,447,452.46</b>, or <b>3%</b>. March saw the fewest offers created (<b>8,061,435</b>) with December having the most (<b>29,537,933</b>) and July being a close second (<b>27,313,359</b>).
</p>

